# DCSE Command Center GitHub containment firewall
# Authorized DCS/DCSE containment write. This file prevents accidental staging of
# secrets, PS/litigation material, local runtime artifacts, vendor folders, caches,
# and large generated assets. It does not delete or move any local files.

# Secrets and credentials
.env
.env.*
*.env
*.env.txt
*.local
*.local.*
